name: The I Ching of Meta-Mark
description:
Facebook has changed its name to Meta, focusing on building the Metaverse——empowering! But how does Mark 'the Cucumber' Zuckerberg come up with such ingenious ideas for new products and technologies? Is it because he has an artificial intelligence? Does he own a quantum oracle to peak into the future? 

No! [insert chuckle] His secret must be the I Ching, that ancient Chinese practice for divining the future through introducing randomness into the system. Cool! 

Now, with this table of 54 words, you too can harness the power of coincidence and talk, think, and innovate like Mark Zucke-di-Zuck Zuckerberg!
